{"tid":2047550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食衞局、衞生署及醫管局將於下午4時半舉行記者會交代最新防疫安排","createTime":"2020-06-02T07:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T08:02:09.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"809f53a30e948185e5ad64492260362de6d9a0d9","tid":2047550,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T07:38:29.000Z","msg":"食衞局、衞生署及醫管局將於下午4時半舉行記者會，據悉，當局將交代有關《若干到港人士強制檢疫規例》（第599C章）的跟進安排，該條例規定曾在內地、澳門及台灣逗留人士，抵港後須強制檢疫14天。該條例有效期至本月7日，若要延長須特首會同行政會議批准。食衞局副秘書長陳偉基日前表示，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">內地、澳門及香港三地政府傾向逐步有序地放寬有關的檢疫限制，初步考慮放寬通過核酸測試者的檢疫安排，有效期為7天，並正研究類似內地的「健康碼」。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200602/S55WQ6SFMBYAYRJGDMGKHXDSOA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200602%2FS55WQ6SFMBYAYRJGDMGKHXDSOA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=bf24cb56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200602%2FS55WQ6SFMBYAYRJGDMGKHXDSOA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=3451a1de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200602/S55WQ6SFMBYAYRJGDMGKHXDSOA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"b2407601d1a4ff104e3bf6bed4679a35849077da","tid":2047550,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T07:39:26.000Z","msg":"大賭博"},{"pid":"a3f55beabd33cca2acd0b74ea254b7280861e2d6","tid":2047550,"uid":2455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T07:40:54.000Z","msg":"